      "key": "elm:3.3:def:Accreditation",
      "kind": "definition",
      "path": "",
      "description": "The quality assurance or licensing of an organisation or a qualification. An accreditation instance can be used to specify information about: (1) the quality assurance and/or licensing of an organisation, (2) the quality assurance and/or licensing of an organisation with respect to a specific qualification.",
